# Copy to .env.release in the repo root (gitignored).
# Only needed for signed builds or GitHub upload — not for a plain local bundle build.

# --- Local build only (Linux / macOS / Windows on that machine) ---
# Nothing required. Either omit this file entirely or run:
#   ./scripts/release.sh
#   scripts\release.cmd                 # Windows Command Prompt / PowerShell
#   ./scripts/release-macos.sh           # explicit macOS launcher
#   ./scripts/release.sh --linux-arch all   # Linux: amd64 + arm64 deb/rpm (+ AppImage on native CPU)
# Updater-capable releases need TAURI_SIGNING_PRIVATE_KEY below. This is separate
# from Apple/Windows code-signing certificates, which can stay unset for now.
# macOS: universal build (Apple Silicon + Intel) is automatic.
# Linux AppImage for the non-native arch: use CI arm/x64 runners or build on that hardware.
# Arch amd64 cross for arm64 deb/rpm: sudo pacman -S aarch64-linux-gnu-gcc
# The script sets NO_STRIP=1 on Linux automatically (AppImage on Arch).

# --- Tauri updater signatures (.sig next to installers) ---
# Generate once: cargo tauri signer generate -w ~/.tauri/blxcode.key
# Put the printed public key into src-tauri/tauri.conf.json > plugins.updater.pubkey.
# TAURI_SIGNING_PRIVATE_KEY can be the key file path or the key contents (base64).
# TAURI_SIGNING_PRIVATE_KEY_PATH=".tauri/blxcode.key"
# TAURI_SIGNING_PRIVATE_KEY="/home/you/.tauri/blxcode.key"
# TAURI_SIGNING_PRIVATE_KEY_PASSWORD=""   # only if the key file is encrypted

# --- macOS distribution (optional; passed through to cargo tauri build) ---
# APPLE_CERTIFICATE=""
# APPLE_CERTIFICATE_PASSWORD=""
# APPLE_SIGNING_IDENTITY="Developer ID Application: …"
# APPLE_ID=""
# APPLE_PASSWORD=""          # app-specific password
# APPLE_TEAM_ID=""

# --- Windows code signing (optional) ---
# TAURI_WINDOWS_SIGNING_CERTIFICATE=""
# TAURI_WINDOWS_SIGNING_CERTIFICATE_PASSWORD=""

# --- GitHub upload / tag push overrides (optional) ---
# Detected from git upstream (origin-2 → Bitslix/BLXCode) when unset.
# RELEASE_GIT_REMOTE_OVERRIDE="origin-2"
# RELEASE_GH_REPO_OVERRIDE="Bitslix/BLXCode"
